"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block pha drugH1Div\" id=\"F9611376\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
"    <span class=\"drugH1\">",
"     Mechanism of Action",
"    </span>",
"    <p style=\"text-indent:0em;display:inline\">",
"     Inhibits DNA-gyrase in susceptible organisms; inhibits relaxation of supercoiled DNA and promotes breakage of double-stranded DNA",
"    </p>",
"   </div>",
"   <div class=\"block phk drugH1Div\" id=\"F9611379\" xmlns=\"file://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">",
